sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Usuario titular
  participant FE as Front postventa
  participant OTP as Solicitud código OTP
  participant Mail as Correo OTP
  participant V as Verificar código OTP
  participant API as Risk items API

  Note over OTP,API: Rutas: /api/postsales/v1/auth/otp/request, /auth/otp/verify y /risk-items/…

  U->>FE: Introduce email
  FE->>OTP: Email
  OTP->>OTP: RPC postsales_risk_item_ids<br/>by_holder_email
  OTP->>Mail: Envía código
  U->>FE: Introduce código
  FE->>V: email + código
  V-->>FE: JWT post-sales
  FE->>API: Authorization Bearer JWT
  API-->>U: Datos / actualizaciones<br/>permitidas
